PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-7/297, which authorized the leasing of a parcel of land at CALGARY INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT to MEDINA DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION, by reducing the size of the site to be leased, reducing the rental fees accordingly, and postponing the date on which the lease shall commence.
